 KOS}}</ref>\n*[[Brian Schatz]], U.S. Senator from Hawaii<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/GreenfieldIowa/status/1233818627956146177|title=Thanks, Senator! Glad you think Saturdays are for flipping the Senate, too. It's going to take all of us to win here in Iowa - chip in: https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tg-february-eom?refcode=tw0229&amount=17\u00a0\u2026https://twitter.com/brianschatz/status/1233808528831201285\u00a0\u2026|first=Theresa|last=Greenfield|date=February 29, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Abby Finkenauer]], U.S. Representative for [[Iowa's 1st congressional district]]<ref name=\"Meyer\"/>\n* [[Dave Loebsack]], U.S. Representative for [[Iowa's 2nd congressional district]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.desmoinesregister.com/story/news/politics/2019/06/25/theresa-greenfield-dave-loebsack-democrat-primary-senate-race-election-jd-scholten-2020-joni-ernst/1559896001/ |title=Theresa Greenfield nets endorsement from Rep. Dave Loebsack in Democratic Senate primary |last=Opsahl |first=Robin|date=June 25, 2019 |website=Des Moines Register}}</ref>\n;Individual\n*Amber Gustafson, former candidate for the [[Iowa Senate]] in 2018<ref name=\"Endorsement Alert!\"/>\n;Organizations\n* [[Brady Campaign]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Brown |first1=Kris |title=Brady Endorses Theresa Greenfield for U.S. Senate: Iowa Needs A Common-sense Champion|url=https://www.bradyunited.org/press-releases/brady-endorses-theresa-greenfield-for-u-s-senate-iowa-needs-a-common-sense-champion |website=Brady |date=January 8, 2020}}</ref>\n* [[Democratic Senatorial Campaign Committee|DSCC]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dscc.org/news/dscc-endorses-theresa-greenfield-in-iowa-senate-campaign/|title=DSCC Endorses Theresa Greenfield in Iowa Senate Campaign|date=June 6, 2019|website=DSCC: Democratic Senatorial Campaign Committee}}</ref>\n* [[EMILY's List]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.emilyslist.org/news/entry/emilys-list-endorses-theresa-greenfield-for-u.s.-senate-in-iowa |title=EMILY's List Endorses Th