tations could be repurchased by Nexstar for a lower cost \"[with] significantly less regulatory push-back\" under the current political climate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2019/04/03/marshall-broadcasting-group-claims-in-lawsuit-that.html|title=Marshall Broadcasting Group claims Nexstar 'undermined' prospects in new suit|last=Butler|first=Anna|date=2019-04-03|website=Dallas Business Journal|access-date=2019-04-04}}</ref><ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/biz/news/nexstar-sued-black-owned-tv-company-1203179793/|title=Nexstar Accused of Sabotaging Black-Owned TV Station Group|last=Maddaus|first=Gene|date=2019-04-03|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2019-04-04}}</ref>\n\nOn December 3, 2019, Marshall Broadcasting Group filed for [[Chapter 11]] bankruptcy protection.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/houston/news/2019/12/26/the-week-in-bankruptcies-7-companies-file-for.html|title=The week in bankruptcies: 7 companies file for bankruptcy protection in Houston|date=2019-12-26|website=Houston Business Journal|access-date=2019-12-29}}</ref>\n\n==Stations==\nCurrent Marshall Broadcasting Group properties include:\n\n{| class=\"toccolours\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse\"\n|- style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\"\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| [[City of License]] / [[Media market|Market]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| Station\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| Channel<br>[[Virtual channel|TV]] ([[Digital terrestrial television|RF]])\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| Owned Since\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| Current Affiliation\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"| [[Nexstar Media Group|Nexstar]] Station(s)<br>(Network Affiliation)\n|- style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\"\n| [[Davenport, Iowa]] / [[Quad Cities]]\n| '''[[KLJB]]'''\n| 18 (49)\n| December 1, 